data.description: -Perfect Starter Home or Investment Property- Truly wonderful home in Northeast Visalia. 3 bed / 2 bath with large welcoming living room, spacious dining area and well situated kitchen. The bedroom are roomy, and nicely cared for. WIth an especially large master bedroom. Newer laminate flooring throughout the home, creates a fresh welcoming feel. Fully enclosed yard provides serene space to relax or entertain. The grounds have an inviting pool to cool off in during the summer, and hot tube to enjoy year round.Ideally located near shopping, dining, and entertainment. Just a short drive to charming downtown Visalia.Property will have the exterior painted as part of the HOA dues.
